These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: sudoku, filmmaking
Job: bartender, engineer
1. Job:bartender is in an even position##4
2. Job:engineer == Hobby:filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | sudoku |
| Job     | engineer    | bartender   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: iced-tea, fanta
Sport: rugby, handball
1. Sport:rugby is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:fanta is on the left of Beverage:iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | fanta | iced-tea        |
| Sport      | rugby  | handball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
